items.title: Overwatch 2: Sigma Guide (Tips, Abilities, And More)
items.text: Sigma was a late entry in the series but he was a strong one. The concept of tanking from a distance is an understandably tough one to flesh out; if he's not on the front, is he truly a tank? Why would enemies focus on him over his squishy teammates? Overwatch 2 experts can answer that question.
